{"tid":885620,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人真係咁易放得低？","createTime":"2018-11-01T12:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T13:29:16.000Z","uid":4717,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"53d3a547bdbc29190b1418c26df9d4d93ad7631c","tid":885620,"uid":4717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T12:57:16.000Z","msg":"各位<br />\n我同我女朋友散咗個幾星期，我放低唔到佢，原因係因為我態度成日都唔好，佢同我性格好似，但佢一直就我，就到冇咗自己，佢氹我氹到攰，慢慢心淡，佢呢架話想自己一個。<br />\n係呢段時間，我剪片俾佢又試過，去佢屋企樓下搵佢又試過，講到大家喊哂，嗰幾日佢話鐘意，但可能大家真係唔夾，但呢架，佢同我講話冇feel，感覺變咗，我呢架好後悔，我好清楚佢影響得我好深，佢更加係我成世最愛嘅人，即使我將來點都好，我都覺得我唔會再咁愛一個人，佢呢架間唔中都仲有hea覆我，但可能只係出於唔想我咁，唔食唔訓，我為咗佢，拜神，求個天都做過哂，我知道冇咗佢，我呢架只係求一次機會，俾我再好好去珍惜佢。"},{"pid":"089f373c2ed7370d208eed1f8c50a57884d08191","tid":885620,"uid":195444,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T12:59:20.000Z","msg":"你係Nigga？"},{"pid":"46e6d0158f7a102c6f8278351a1c3b195f4e122c","tid":885620,"uid":4717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"089f373c2ed7370d208eed1f8c50a57884d08191","tid":885620,"uid":195444,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T12:59:20.000Z","msg":"你係Nigga？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"？唔明"},{"pid":"81fc3821d9b3fb2dc9fbb7ea690f25e678143eab","tid":885620,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:00:47.000Z","msg":"唔食豬同牛"},{"pid":"0281ed047bcafdf476647e7721e22a988c7f8a84","tid":885620,"uid":52188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 順其自然吧"},{"pid":"68ceb253bd0fca761892918e422a17f71e2791cf","tid":885620,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:12:43.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人唔拍拖<br />\n係因為好驚再失去果一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cb5e39f4389089255c36256ad5317ef767df4d","tid":885620,"uid":48579,"like